name: コズミックウィッチ/ KOZUMIKKUU~ITCH
description: Cosmic Witch. She is half yūrei and half Yōkai creature. She can remain in ghost or living human mode at will. She has the power of clairvoyance, and she grants you various wishes, but you must comply with her requests, some somewhat uncomfortable such as walking naked on a busy street. She's very dangerous if you don't fulfill her whims: she could leave you blind or dumb, or ruin your existence for life. Weird Japanese Toys, 2021.
